If some hosts use the same area environment and application.
You can use this script and write them in a file.
If just one host you can use command line and options..

ohtpl_area_XXX
ohtpl_env_XXX
bhtpl/htpl_app_XXX_XXX

hosts.txt format eg:
area:
environment:
application:
parents:
ROMIOAPP0005           10.196.73.32    
romioapp0005.ww.corp   romioapp0005.ww.corp
